        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1331585924" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4602765522716355820">The Sexy Part of The Bible is like nothing I, or probably anyone else, has ever read.<br/>Near impossible to define and constantly surprising, Kola Boof crafts a story charged with sexuality, issues of race and threads of cosmic violence and rebirth.<br/>Eternity Frankenheimer is an incomparable literary heroine whose story is so far from what is usually seen in the culture that it illuminates truths about society itself and what it means to be human, a woman, and black.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


